WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:06.271
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining me today. I have my sweetheart with me again.

00:00:06.272 --> 00:00:22.473
I have a very sobering word, is what I want to call it, for what the Lord has given me today. It's very heavy; it's correction for the body.

00:00:22.474 --> 00:00:43.700
But whenever you get a word like this, and you see into the future, and you see hearts, there was so much the Lord showed me driving around when I was praying over our city today.

00:00:43.701 --> 00:00:54.994
Quite frankly, I don't even know where to start or how to even bring this up because of how correction was said and what the Lord said.

00:00:54.995 --> 00:01:11.199
So, I'm asking the Holy Spirit for help right now. I want to deliver it accurately, and I want to deliver it with none of Brandon, all of Jesus.

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:22.569
Okay, so this is what I saw. I saw a great economic crisis coming.

00:01:22.570 --> 00:01:30.026
I haven't seen this in a while: an economic 1930s-style crash on steroids.

00:01:30.027 --> 00:01:39.512
All I've seen was this blessing, but the Lord brought the blessing in with the crash again.

00:01:39.513 --> 00:01:47.438
And as I was driving around, I could see—the Lord said, 'What you see is poor now.

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:53.024
There will be no middle class in the days ahead. There will be no middle class.

00:01:53.025 --> 00:02:14.155
There will be poor, and there'll be extreme poor, and then there will be rich.'He said, 'What you see right now—as you see what you consider the people who work at McDonald's, Taco Bell employees, maybe making a little bit above minimum wage, would be considered the middle class in the days ahead.

00:02:14.156 --> 00:02:42.791
And what we consider poor will be so poor that I saw what I can only describe as poverty like I've never seen before in America.'As I was driving around, I was having an open-eyed vision, and I was actually seeing the way it was in future time, in real-time, driving around.

00:02:42.792 --> 00:02:51.589
And I can tell you, I've never done this before. I could see tent cities of homeless people walking around.

00:02:51.590 --> 00:02:59.119
Like when you go to LA and you see a homeless street like Skid Row, this was everywhere.

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:16.139
And I can tell you, I saw the housing crisis coming again with people not being able to pay their mortgages—not just a couple hundred people, I'm talking thousands upon thousands of people not being able to pay their mortgages or their car loans.

00:03:16.140 --> 00:03:25.536
And there was foreclosure everywhere, to the point where I was wondering who was not foreclosing on their houses.

00:03:25.537 --> 00:03:33.049
Like I said, there was no middle class. There was poor, there was extreme poor, and then there was the rich.

00:03:33.050 --> 00:03:41.129
But there was a Robin Hood mentality that I saw. There was such a hatred towards the rich.

00:03:41.130 --> 00:03:55.309
And what I saw in rich neighborhoods was that they had security, armed security, around their houses and around their property at all times because the people would loot them and steal from them.

00:03:55.310 --> 00:04:07.839
And there were certain streets that we were driving down that I knew, that the Lord showed me in the future, it would not be safe for women to go on those streets.

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:23.918
To the point where right now there are malls there, there are nice restaurants there, and the Lord showed me that there would be times in the future that you could not be a woman and go down these streets at night at all.

00:04:23.919 --> 00:04:35.966
As I drove around, he said to me, 'Woe, America, I have favored you above all other nations with prosperity. I have held you in my hand.

00:04:35.967 --> 00:04:48.478
I have held you in my hand.'It was the way that the blessing was on America—the favor and the blessing that has been on our nation.

00:04:48.479 --> 00:04:56.034
And I saw, as I was driving around, a shaking of finances beyond anything I've ever seen before.

00:04:56.035 --> 00:05:21.999
But he talked to me about the wave of blessing, this window of opportunity, and how he said, 'Brandon, even I, even my wife, we've got to come up even higher in the fire to listen to what he's asking and instructing us to do.'I saw people fleeing the city again, and masses going to rural land and having places of getaway because of how bad it was.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:27.938
I saw people pillaging grocery stores, pillaging farmers'fields and tractors.

00:05:27.939 --> 00:05:37.851
I'm talking it looked like something out of a Mad Max movie, the way the people were acting.

00:05:37.852 --> 00:05:48.559
And like I said, I've never seen poverty like I saw in these visions as I was driving around praying over our city.

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:53.472
This is Oklahoma; I can't even imagine what it looked like up north.

00:05:53.473 --> 00:06:05.800
But the Lord said, 'You took part of the word that I said to you about there being glory events instead of sporting events, and you just kind of bypassed it.

00:06:05.801 --> 00:06:24.959
You didn't think into what I was telling you, that the people would not have finances to go to a sporting event in the days ahead, and that these major sporting teams would have to file bankruptcy because they were not able to pay their big sports teams their salaries.

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:49.038
The major contracts that were signed concerning some of these major players, they won't be able to afford them because the teams will not have support from the fans.'So, I saw again the Lord speaking to me about major teams, sporting event teams, that will file bankruptcy because of what's coming in the near future.

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:58.283
We have a window of opportunity the Lord is giving us to listen to him for the wealth transfer. What qualifies you for the wealth transfer?

00:06:58.284 --> 00:07:11.216
And the Lord gave you specific instructions about sowing and what cost you something versus bucket plunkers where you just give a couple hundred bucks and you think, 'Well, I qualified for the wealth transfer,'and the Lord said, 'That's not what qualifies.

00:07:11.216 --> 00:07:20.282
The one percent will walk in this.'And I saw again today the heart of the church as a whole.

00:07:20.283 --> 00:07:24.637
I'm not going to say it's each individual person. I'm saying as a whole.

00:07:24.638 --> 00:07:39.758
Okay? It's fair; this is fair. I saw an apple that looked gorgeous on the outside. And this apple was just juicy looking.

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:52.879
But the Lord said, 'I want to take you to the core of what this fruit really is and the fruit of the church as a whole in America.'And it was rotten at the core; it was rotten on the inside.

00:07:52.880 --> 00:08:02.851
Everything that was displayed on the inside looked like rotten sludge; it was black and putrid and nasty, and it was just so disgusting.

00:08:02.852 --> 00:08:09.315
But the further it went on the outside, and the display of what it tried to display itself, was beautiful and lush.

00:08:09.316 --> 00:08:14.722
But when you took a bite out of it, it wasn't the first bite that was bad.

00:08:14.723 --> 00:08:18.553
It was after you bit it several times and then you got to the center.

00:08:18.554 --> 00:08:27.302
And the closer you got to the center of the core of the church, it was rotten. And the Lord said, 'I want you to see what I see.

00:08:27.303 --> 00:08:43.038
I want you to see what comes before me as you ask for revival, but yet I'm trying to bring healing at a certain church, but you're too concerned about timeframes.

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:54.430
It's not convenient. And what I'm about to do in this end-time outpouring will not be convenient to you—the 30-minute services, maybe the hour services.

00:08:54.431 --> 00:09:01.392
Well, you know, we had service two days ago, but you know, we prayed for the revival and a couple of people got saved.

00:09:01.393 --> 00:09:13.491
And yet we are interceding and we're wanting so much, but yet we want to give so little.'And the Lord showed me there's so much in the hearts of the leaders.

00:09:13.492 --> 00:09:26.398
I saw people that were something in the past trying to be Sauls, asking to present themselves as if the anointing and the glory was still there.

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:36.398
But the Lord said, 'It's a great Ichabod coming. There's a great Ichabod coming on a lot of these people, and they don't even know the glory has departed.

00:09:36.399 --> 00:09:49.679
The glory has departed. Their heart is far from me.'What you're about to see is this scripture come to full manifestation, and the church has never seen this before.

00:09:49.680 --> 00:10:00.958
And so I want you to read this scripture, baby. It says, 'And because iniquity shall abound, the love of many shall wax cold.'And that's Matthew.

00:10:00.959 --> 00:10:16.843
'But he that shall endure until the end, the same shall be saved.'And this gospel of the kingdom shall be preached in all the world for a witness unto all nations, and then the end shall come. So we're at that place right now.

00:10:16.844 --> 00:10:35.272
What He started talking to us about is that the love of many will wax cold, and He said you're going to see pillaging and you're going to see people in the body of Christ do things that you never thought you would see, with a turning on people.

00:10:35.273 --> 00:10:50.073
I saw it. When He used that scripture, I saw the way it was with people, and the way they were not safe to go to Walmart. It was rough. The visions that I had today were rough.

00:10:50.074 --> 00:10:58.396
And I'm telling you, it shook me because He was talking about all these people who say they're all in, who are in upper leadership.

00:10:58.397 --> 00:11:18.898
They've been there, and they have this sense of, 'I've been there, I've done that, I have had the glory on me in the past.'And they want to pretend that they're still on the vine, but the heart of who they really are has waxed cold, and they are no longer that vessel that is on fire for Him.

00:11:18.899 --> 00:11:44.378
They have an entitlement: 'I've been there, I've done that, I'm qualified.'But I saw a church through the Father's eyes that was no longer desperate and hungry anymore; they were entitled.

00:11:44.379 --> 00:12:12.799
'You have an hour to do this healing room service, two hours at the most, but if it goes over that, it's time for my bedtime.'But people are so desperate for a touch, and you're a leader, and yet you qualify yourself by a clock, saying, 'Well, it's too long.'And the Lord said, 'Brandon, what's about to happen will not be convenient.

00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:25.180
A shaking to awaken is coming to America. You're about to see something that you never thought you would see.'And I'm telling you, from sea to shining sea, we will have a great revival.

00:12:25.181 --> 00:12:31.516
But there is no urgency in the church. The Lord is showing me that.

00:12:31.517 --> 00:12:43.515
I'm not saying everybody—I don't want to lump everybody in the same category because there are some of you who are very urgent, very hungry, desperate for a move of God.

00:12:43.516 --> 00:12:53.453
But as a whole, from what He was showing me, He is about to shake you out of your comfort zone.

00:12:53.454 --> 00:13:00.368
And He told me, He said, 'A lot of the people that you see, Brandon, are going to go home.

00:13:00.369 --> 00:13:06.805
I'm going to show them the door. They're not going to be behind the pulpit anymore. I'm done.

00:13:06.806 --> 00:13:17.994
And what you thought you got away with in the past through hidden sin...'He said there is an exposing of things beyond anything.

00:13:17.995 --> 00:13:24.917
I saw so many leaders, and He gave me an open-eye vision, and I was going over it, and it was wild.

00:13:24.918 --> 00:13:34.312
I was scanning in the spirit realm, and I was looking at each individual face, and He was showing me the depth inside of them and what He was requiring of them.

00:13:34.312 --> 00:13:44.398
And He said, 'Brandon, there's so much hidden sin and so much compromise that they feel they've gotten away with for so long, and those days are done.

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:53.292
Those days are done of walking in compromise and feeling that you're getting away with something because I didn't do anything about it for so long and you got away.

00:13:53.293 --> 00:14:11.119
You're preaching from the pulpit and you have this open window inside of you that is letting the barnyard animals in,'is what I want to say, with sin and compromise, and you just say, 'Well, it's been okay because I've been doing this for years.'Those days are over.

00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:24.381
And as we go into September, as we go into the fall, there's an acceleration of things beyond anybody's comprehension of what I've seen, and it quite frankly shook me.

00:14:24.382 --> 00:14:32.685
It made me question my walk with Him and say, 'God, search me and know me.

00:14:32.686 --> 00:14:38.103
Make me pure before You, Father, by Your blood.'I run to You, Father.

00:14:38.104 --> 00:14:47.599
As David said, 'As a deer panteth after the water, so my soul longeth for You.'I don't want to play church anymore.

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:56.159
And I'm telling you, I even saw a major hurricane coming, and He warned me about a major hurricane.

00:14:56.160 --> 00:15:06.848
And of this major hurricane, He said, 'This hurricane that's about to hit will be so violent on a major city in Florida.

00:15:06.849 --> 00:15:26.685
I saw a storm surge that was the largest ever recorded coming into a major city.'He said, 'This will make Katrina look like a walk in the park for what I've seen coming.'He said, 'The cup of sin is full before Me concerning the city and sex trafficking.'And He said, 'These cities and the people, there's so much witchcraft.

00:15:26.686 --> 00:15:34.632
There's so much stuff going on in some of these major cities that the cup of sin is full, Brandon, and seedtime and harvest is accelerating.

00:15:34.633 --> 00:15:50.239
And you're about to see a harvest for what they've been sowing.'And I saw a storm surge come into this major city down in Florida that was so massive and so big. I mean, it looked like something out of a movie.

00:15:50.240 --> 00:16:20.638
Fish swimming up—I'm talking dolphins swimming in the city, sharks in the city—a major storm surge because this hurricane was so big, genetically altered through weather warfare, hurricanes like how we just saw a Category 1 go to a Category 5 in just a couple of hours.

00:16:20.639 --> 00:16:27.119
Never has that happened before. It went from this to, bam, 160 mph plus winds.

00:16:27.120 --> 00:16:32.794
Folks, we're in a time like we've never seen before. And He's speaking to me about the hurricanes.

00:16:32.795 --> 00:16:38.003
He's speaking to me about signs in the heavens and the earth, and a shaking to awaken.

00:16:38.004 --> 00:16:43.708
And He said, 'Ride the wave, Brandon. Ride the wave that's about to take place.

00:16:43.709 --> 00:16:53.614
You are about to see a financial outpouring in this time. I saw Jerome Powell. I saw all this stuff incoming with the interest rates.

00:16:53.615 --> 00:17:00.145
I saw, like I said, them seizing houses in the days ahead because the people are not able to pay.

00:17:00.146 --> 00:17:10.476
I saw inflation. I saw Trump printing money—I'm talking like turning the printing press on in the days ahead.

00:17:10.477 --> 00:17:20.140
I saw so much artificial money coming because they realized that the Titanic was sinking and there's nothing they can do to stop it.

00:17:20.141 --> 00:17:28.674
But they're going to tell you everything's better, everything's good, 'We're going to make America great again.'But there is no really making America great again, folks.

00:17:28.675 --> 00:17:36.769
Regardless of what they tell you, I've seen it. The Lord said to me, He said, 'Brandon, America's debt and where we are is at the point of no return.

00:17:36.770 --> 00:17:47.749
Regardless of the tariffs they try to—they say, "We're going to raise tariff prices over here"or "do all this over here, we're going to fix this"—I saw there was no fixing it.

00:17:47.750 --> 00:17:58.875
They will bring in and usher in a one-world currency in the days ahead with a digital dollar, with a digital everything that will line up with the beast system.

00:17:58.876 --> 00:18:06.427
We're headed for the mark of the beast. Do you understand? We're headed for the end of the end.

00:18:06.428 --> 00:18:16.553
It's not about making America great again or making America all this again. We're buying—God's giving us more time—buying time.

00:18:16.554 --> 00:18:25.359
We're staying afloat for you to get your house in order so that you won't be caught off guard if you're listening to Him.

00:18:25.360 --> 00:18:33.162
Woe unto you who have hidden sin and are not listening to the Father's heartbeat right now and listening to the prophets.

00:18:33.163 --> 00:18:42.305
He brought them up like they were of Jeremiah. He said, 'There were so many itching-ear prophets, false prophets prophesying, not My heart.

00:18:42.306 --> 00:18:48.079
But I had Jeremiah Braden saying what I needed him to say. Be My Jeremiah.

00:18:48.080 --> 00:18:53.666
Warn My people what's coming. Tell My people there's a shaking to awaken.

00:18:53.667 --> 00:19:06.479
A major revival is coming.'But what is going to cause the major revival? 'I will not be dealing with a house of compromise.

00:19:06.480 --> 00:19:13.499
I want a purified bride without spot or wrinkle.'But what's going to come is a shaking to awaken His church.

00:19:13.500 --> 00:19:30.338
And it's the leadership that has been in status quo, thinking everything's okay, 'I can dabble in this and I can dabble in that because I've been doing it for so long and there have not been any consequences for my actions.'And the Lord said, "Those days are done, Brandon."He said, "It's coming to a head.

00:19:30.339 --> 00:19:50.613
I saw a mountain that was white-capped that was coming to a head."And he said, "The tip of that thing is about to bust through and you're about to see things that you never dreamed you would see or ever thought of."And I go over this and I go over this to warn you of what the Father's heart is.

00:19:50.614 --> 00:19:55.748
Many people do not know. They're hearing so much itching ears'words.

00:19:55.749 --> 00:20:11.640
And I refuse to be like the prophets of old and not be like a Jeremiah in these last days warning you that something big is coming—shakings to awaken, earthquakes, tsunamis, fearful sights you will see that will bring you to your knees.

00:20:11.641 --> 00:20:19.999
A shaking in the economy beyond anybody's comprehension. But he's given you a window of Trump.

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:23.124
Ride the wave. He said to me again today, "Ride the wave, Brandon.

00:20:23.125 --> 00:20:33.119
Prepare your house. Get ready."He doesn't want his beloved to go through things.

00:20:33.120 --> 00:20:40.202
But what qualifies you to be his beloved? When he said, "You prophesied in my name.

00:20:40.203 --> 00:20:44.277
You laid hands on the sick in my name. You cast out devils in my name.

00:20:44.278 --> 00:20:52.152
Depart from me. I never knew you."He never knew you at all. You were never one of his.

00:20:52.153 --> 00:20:56.098
Your heart was never there. It was always lip service. You weren't all in.

00:20:56.099 --> 00:21:06.239
You weren't sold out. It's not about works. I'm not saying it's about works. But it is about heart.

00:21:06.240 --> 00:21:38.823
There's a difference between working and trying to do something to get the anointing versus my heart is truly for you and I'm desperate for you, versus "I have part of the world and part of it, but I'm going to do lip service because it looks pretty like the apple on the outside and everybody wants to bite the apple, but until they get to the center of who you really are."And I saw so many preachers that had so much pride and so much ego and so much going on on the outside.

00:21:38.824 --> 00:21:46.558
"We're holy. Oh God, let's worship him for 30 minutes."But their heart of who they were was all about me.

00:21:46.559 --> 00:21:55.019
And the Lord said, "You asked so many times to go around some of these people."And he goes, "You know whenever my daughter says, 'Daddy, I want to go over here. I want to do this.

00:21:55.020 --> 00:22:15.250
I want to do that.'And as a father, you say, 'No, I see who those kids really are, and I don't want what's on them getting on you.'"So, you can ask to go around certain people, and you're going, "Man, they're so good on the outside. Boy, they're cool. They're popular.

00:22:15.251 --> 00:22:33.119
I want to be part of them."And the Lord said to me, "I don't want what's on them on you because you don't know the core of who they really are."I'm protecting you just like you protect your kids and you say, "I see through the spirit who they are and you're not going over to their house.

00:22:33.120 --> 00:22:40.270
You're not doing this. You're not doing that."I've done that my whole life over my son, over my daughter. You know, that's just the way we are.

00:22:40.271 --> 00:22:54.959
I don't allow my kids to do certain things because I'm not judging, but it's my job as the father to protect the innocence inside of them because God's given me those children to protect.

00:22:54.960 --> 00:23:03.106
So, what does the Father say about you? "Hey, I want you to do certain things, this and that."And you go, "Well, I haven't had a door open over there.

00:23:03.107 --> 00:23:11.759
I haven't had it."Because he's protecting you because he sees something in them that he doesn't want on you—compromise.

00:23:11.760 --> 00:23:25.303
And he's saying, "I've got to protect that gift inside you because I'm going to use you greatly in the days ahead."And it may feel really lonely. "I feel so abandoned."Sometimes you feel so lonely.

00:23:25.304 --> 00:23:39.245
Sometimes I say, "Where are my friends?"But when I heard Kathryn Kuhlman say she was a person that was always alone, she said, "My social life is zero."And it helped me because I saw a woman that I respect greatly.

00:23:39.246 --> 00:23:46.558
We drove over to where she passed away in the hospital today.

00:23:46.559 --> 00:24:10.095
And when we were driving around in the city, I said, "That's where Sister Kuhlman went home."And I told my kids as we were doing homeschool, I said, "That's where she went home."One of the greatest pioneer women, I would say, of any generation bringing in healing died right there in this hospital.

00:24:10.096 --> 00:24:20.639
I don't know if she went home alone or whatever, but I just reflect on the elders who walked with him.

00:24:20.640 --> 00:24:26.358
And she said, "I was alone most of the time. I was sold out to him.

00:24:26.359 --> 00:24:36.158
There's a place of dying, a refining fire."And I said, "God, help me.

00:24:36.159 --> 00:24:45.835
I don't want what's in this world."Especially after the open-eyed vision that I had that lasted for over an hour.

00:24:45.836 --> 00:24:59.839
It shook me because it's so easy to get over into that state of compromise because the world is shiny.

00:24:59.840 --> 00:25:07.519
It's so easy to get over into that Hollywood stuff where he's not at all.

00:25:07.520 --> 00:25:22.197
He's that still small voice that draws you close to him daily, that is looking for you and saying, "Will you just sit at my feet?"It may not look glamorous at the time because it's the place of surrender.

00:25:22.198 --> 00:25:35.384
It's that place of death. It's that place where it doesn't look popular, but that's where he's at. And all I want is him.

00:25:35.385 --> 00:25:47.222
And in these last days, for what I saw of so many leaders upon our nation, they have no idea of what's truly coming. A lot of them, they're so full of themselves.

00:25:47.223 --> 00:26:00.402
And the Lord said to me, "Brandon, I'm shaking a lot of these people right out the door."And the people you see in the future will be people with new faces.

00:26:00.403 --> 00:26:05.599
They won't be people like you see in a lot of this Hollywood stuff.

00:26:05.600 --> 00:26:11.027
I saw a humbling coming, ladies and gentlemen, that I'm not happy with.

00:26:11.028 --> 00:26:17.119
It won't just be about America. It will be a worldwide humbling because it's a worldwide revival.

00:26:17.120 --> 00:26:27.999
And it will be a glorious church rising in Brush Arbor churches, Holy Ghost Woodstocks in the country.

00:26:28.000 --> 00:26:35.328
Maybe not so much because these big mega churches, they foreclose on them. I saw a lot of them foreclosed.

00:26:35.329 --> 00:26:49.439
I saw a lot of them that could not pay the mortgage on their building because they were so debt heavy and there was not enough money coming in because the church wasn't able to give like they used to because they were just trying to pay their bills because they weren't listening.

00:26:49.440 --> 00:26:57.152
How many times have I said it's like Sodom and Gomorrah? Lot was in there and he didn't know what was coming because he became so familiar with Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:26:57.153 --> 00:27:05.678
Abraham was the only one that knew it was coming. Why? Because he was close to the Father.

00:27:05.679 --> 00:27:11.439
He was a friend of God. The Bible says that Abraham was a friend of God.

00:27:11.440 --> 00:27:21.678
And God came and shared his secret things. I refuse to not be a friend of God.

00:27:21.679 --> 00:27:27.255
There's nothing else that matters to me. I'd give it all away, every dollar.

00:27:27.256 --> 00:27:35.614
I said, "My God, whatever it takes to be close to your heart in these last days."Last night it was awesome.

00:27:35.615 --> 00:27:43.425
Diana was getting up off the floor and her back was hurting so bad. She said, "Baby, my back hurts getting off this floor.

00:27:43.426 --> 00:27:52.772
Will you please pray for me?"And I grabbed a hold of her and the power of God went out of my hands and went all through her body.

00:27:52.773 --> 00:28:01.038
And she said, "Your hands are getting so hot."And the glory of the Lord filled her up and she felt it all night long.

00:28:01.039 --> 00:28:05.540
And I don't take any of the... it's not about Brandon, but I want to tell you this.

